{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-11208/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-11208"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:12:08"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["single shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Woman pours mushrooms into teapot"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-11208","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-11208"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/canvas/1/abdb2976-86df-4152-86c5-583b59ea8b59","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:08:01.207Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma is seen from within the tea kettle. Her face is blurred by the liquid and becomes wavy when she pours the ground mushroom in. This strange perspective and her warped visage suggest that something is off—the poisoning.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Sima Movaghati furthermore observes that this shot paints Alma in a witchy light, as if she is concocting her poison in a cauldron (Movaghati, “Bluebeard Meets Ivy,” 732).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11208/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:461.7721518987342,246.32911392405066,821.6033755274264,739.2405063291139"}}}]}]}]}